headline: Nike's NFL Partnership Gets Major Boost With 10-Year Deal, Stock Gains
summary: Nike, Inc. (NYSE:NKE) shares are trading higher on Wednesday. Today, the company declared a 10-year partnership extension with the National Football League (NFL). Building on 12 years of successful collaboration, Nike will continue as the exclusive provider of uniforms, sideline, practice, and baselayer apparel for all 32 NFL teams. headline: NIKE, Inc. & NFL Extend Long-Standing Partnership Through 2038
summary: DALLAS, December 11, 2024--NIKE, Inc. (NYSE: NKE) and the National Football League (NFL) today announced a landmark 10-year partnership extension, cementing their commitment to shaping the future of football and driving growth, innovation, and progress across the sport.
